description: Payne, who came to fame as a teen in the massively popular British boy band One Direction, died in Buenos Aires after falling from his hotel balcony, according to reporting by the Associated Press.
title: Liam Payne, former member of One Direction, dies at 31

description: Guitarist John Scofield picks 10 of his favorite tracks from his own catalog and shares the stories behind them as he celebrates 50 years of recorded music.
title: 50 years in 10 tracks: A career-spanning playlist from John Scofield

description: Michel Houellebecq is a controversial literary superstar. His new book, Annihilation, centers on a middle-aged Paris bureaucrat in a sexless marriage. It's slow to start, but still holds surprises.
title: A polarizing, provocative French novelist says he’s written his last book

description: The British band hasn't had a chart-topping album in a decade, but it pulled out all the stops to promote its latest, Moon Music, including selling more than a dozen different versions of the album.
title: Coldplay tops album chart, thanks to old-fashioned sales and modern tricks
